{"tid":1754982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"感覺兩u 戰役搞到勇武收咗皮","createTime":"2019-11-25T11:47:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T14:26:28.000Z","uid":59450,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"6d988ec4ec72b6281624933e25c9f4e4293eab2a","tid":1754982,"uid":59450,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:47:24.000Z","msg":"可能係區選啦，大家都休息咗成個禮拜，亦都少咗人去救poly。<br />\n<br />\n唔知係咪因為好多最前線勇武都受傷/被捕，好似冇咩人再出黎，或者吹雞。我身邊啲fd都叫唔郁，就算出黎做和理非佢哋都唔肯join。可能覺得，就算和理都會被告，咁不如出黎打，但係又冇人叫出嚟打&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n我希望大家唔好放棄住，如果呢排靜一陣都ok，不過要諗下勇武如果唔出嚟打陣地、開花既話，會唔會改變打法仲好玩。<br />\n<br />\n雖然我自己都未諗到要做咩，都希望大家快啲叉足電，我地要有新一波行動了。"},{"pid":"5dafab651728ac409c791530d847d55b0934cd13","tid":1754982,"uid":301079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:57:06.000Z","msg":"全香港有幾多手足喺度呀？你以為咁快就GG？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91444f13f5949932d19bd947265243ec4364418","tid":1754982,"uid":59450,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5dafab651728ac409c791530d847d55b0934cd13","tid":1754982,"uid":301079,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:57:06.000Z","msg":"全香港有幾多手足喺度呀？你以為咁快就GG？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:05:21.000Z","msg":"勇武嘅話真係有限，如果計埋識打果啲仲少，cu poly都真係見盡精英<br />\n<br />\n希望佢地已經準備緊大單野啦😉"},{"pid":"74d92ac263e09b61dc24ff5b53eb9d69516ce4ba","tid":1754982,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:07:27.000Z","msg":"上個星期消耗太大<br />\n<br />\n先將目標放係星期六，日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b20aeeb5e2825891074e931659d0a807b8376d49","tid":1754982,"uid":49955,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T14:08:18.000Z","msg":"和非手足頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16f2098125552eb544021028da5a8f63e2731826","tid":1754982,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"ci